title: Wholesale Price of Plate Glass, 3-5 Square Feet for New York
notes:
Prices Are For Unsilvered, 3-5 Square Feet Glazing Area, Price, F.O.B. New York. 1906-1917 Data Are First Of Month Prices, 1918-1931 Data Are Daily Averages, 1932-1941 Are Averages Of Tuesday Quotations. Source: Bls Bulletins

This NBER data series m04131 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
